                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4535" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0653</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8219 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">如何委托与代理？ —基于上海家化控制权的变更事件的分析 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to entrust and agent?—Analysis of change events based on control right of Shanghai Jiahua </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李唯滨，赵迪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李唯滨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海家化；中国平安；控制权争夺；绝对控股</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shanghai Jiahua; China Ping An; control struggle; absolute holding</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海家化作为我国⽇化⾏业的翘楚，在⼀百多年的公司发展过程中，克服重重困难逐渐成⻓为⼀个引领中国⻛尚、承载⺠族梦想的家化企业。本案例运用公司治理理论以上海家化两次股权变更事件为研究对象，研究了上海家化大股东在相对控股与绝对控股前后对企业的绩效的影响。分析了上海家化首次控制权变更后管理层与大股东的矛盾产生的原因及对企业价值产生的影响。重点研究了⼤股东通过要约收购实现绝对控股后与新任管理层合作进行价值创造过程，探讨了管理层与控股股东在“制定新战略，寻求新定位，开发新品牌，采⽤新代⾔⼈”等这四个⽅⾯所开展协同合作机制，并依据公司治理理论研究了上海家化在控制权变更中委托代理问题对企业价值创造的影响。案例研究表明，在控制权变更中，大股东与管理层的分工合作机制是提升企业绩效实现价值创造的重要因素，而大股东的绝对控股有利于改善了分工合作机制的效率。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">hanghai Jiahua, as the leader of China&#39;s Jiahua industry, has overcome many difficulties in the development of the company for more than 100 years and gradually become a Jiahua enterprise that leads China&#39;s fashion and carries the dream of the Chinese people. In this case, the corporate governance theory is used to study the impact of major shareholders of Shanghai Jiahua on corporate performance before and after the relative holding and absolute controlling shares. This paper analyzes the causes of the contradiction between the management and the major shareholders after the first change of control right of Shanghai Jiahua and its impact on the enterprise value. This paper focuses on the process of value creation by the cooperation between shareholders and the new management after the acquisition by offer. It also discusses the cooperative mechanism between the management and the controlling shareholders in &quot;formulating new strategies, seeking new positions, developing new brands, and adopting the new generation&quot;. It also studies the Shanghai Jiahua Committee in the change of control rights according to the theory of corporate governance The impact of trust agency on the value creation of enterprises. The case study shows that in the change of control right, the division and cooperation mechanism between the major shareholders and the management is an important factor to enhance the enterprise performance and realize value creation, and the absolute holding of the major shareholders is conducive to improving the efficiency of the division and cooperation mechanism.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">控制权变更、绝对控股、委托代理问题、控制权</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
